    • Uses of AThornSecException in core.profile

      Methods in core.profile that throw AThornSecException 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      protected java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getInstalled()
      This is units relating to installing software for this profile
      protected java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getLiveConfig()
      This is Units for configurations you expect to change regularly, e.g.
      protected java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getLiveFirewall()
      This is probably the firewall method you're looking for.
      protected java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getPersistentConfig()
      Expecting the configuration to change regularly? Put it in AStructuredProfile.getLiveConfig()!
      protected java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getPersistentFirewall()
      You almost certainly mean AStructuredProfile.getLiveFirewall().
      java.util.Set<IUnit> AStructuredProfile.getUnits()
      Returns a Set of all units related to this profile.
